<p>print(Zend_Date::isDate('20.10.09/1945', 'dd.MM.YY/HHmm') ? 'valid' : 'invalid');
print("\n");</p>

<p>print(Zend_Date::isDate('20.10.09/19:45', 'dd.MM.YY/HH:mm') ? 'valid' : 'invalid');
print("\n");</p>

<p>is expected to print:</p>

<p>valid
valid</p>

<p>However, I get:</p>

<p>invalid
valid</p>

